OL,3,CUK economy saw no growth in month
OL,4,Cbefore Iran war, figures show
OL,6,FThe UK saw zero economic growth in
OL,7,FJanuary, putting further pressure on
OL,8,Fthe government as it faces the fallout
OL,9,Fof the US-Israeli war with Iran.
OL,11,FThe 0% growth was lower than expected
OL,12,Fand followed 0.1% growth in December,
OL,13,Faccording to the Office for National
OL,14,FStatistics (ONS), which said the
OL,15,Foverall picture of the UK economy was
OL,16,F"subdued".
OL,18,FChancellor Rachel Reeves said: "Our
OL,19,Feconomic plan is the right one, but I
OL,20,Fknow there is more to do.
OL,26,@zD@`OU
