OL,3,CUK economy saw no growth in month
OL,4,Cbefore Iran war, figures show
OL,6,F"In an uncertain world, we are
OL,7,Fbuilding a stronger and more secure
OL,8,Feconomy by cutting the cost of living,
OL,9,Fcutting national debt and creating the
OL,10,Fconditions for growth to make all
OL,11,Fparts of the country better off."
OL,13,FThe service sector (by far the largest
OL,14,Fshare of the UK economy) showed no
OL,15,Fgrowth, while production fell 0.1% and
OL,16,Fconstruction grew by 0.2%.
