OL,3,CUK economy saw no growth in month
OL,4,Cbefore Iran war, figures show
OL,6,FThe Labour government has placed
OL,7,Fgrowth at the heart of its strategy
OL,8,Ffor this Parliament, but so far has
OL,9,Fstruggled to kick-start a sluggish
OL,10,Feconomy.
OL,12,FThe war in Iran also threatens to
OL,13,Fderail any plans to boost economic
OL,14,Fgrowth, with economists predicting the
OL,15,Fspike in oil prices could have a
OL,16,Fdirect impact on the UK's inflation
OL,17,Frate.
